    "settings": [{"type":"paragraph","content":"Section design by GemPages. [Click here to start design](https://admin.shopify.com/store/sheikhashadul/apps/gempages-cro/app/shopify/edit?pageType=GP_ARTICLE&editorId=607381796862034487&sectionId=607393004713411158)"},{"type":"select","label":"Section Preload","id":"section_preload","options":[{"label":"On","value":"true"},{"label":"Off","value":"false"},{"label":"Off Lazy Script","value":"off_lazy_script"}],"default":"false"},{"type":"text","label":"Checksum","id":"checksum"},{"type":"html","id":"gg5YMEI5zwl_text","label":"gg5YMEI5zwl_text","default":"And Today, I Will Share This Secret... Every Detail That You Need To Know If You’re Over 30...With You."},{"type":"html","id":"ggnaf3mekjw_text","label":"ggnaf3mekjw_text","default":"<p>Why am I doing this?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggQcA0MaGwq_text","label":"ggQcA0MaGwq_text","default":"<p>Firstly, the waiting list to see me personally in Korea is currently over a year long. And that's with me working 6 days a week and taking almost no vacations!</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggpOs3FHNdg_text","label":"ggpOs3FHNdg_text","default":"<p>It's become obvious to me that if I'm going to reach my goal of helping the millions of women who struggle with loose and sagging skin, deep wrinkles, and uneven texture... <strong>I need to spread the word right now about the true cause of aging skin, so women across America can finally take back control of their appearance.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gguFSTrTkfD_text","label":"gguFSTrTkfD_text","default":"<p>We live in a world where skincare companies and beauty brands don't provide real anti-aging solutions...they just provide temporary fixes...</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggGezG8trT7_text","label":"ggGezG8trT7_text","default":"<p>Waiting for us to get desperate so they can charge us for expensive creams and treatments that only mask our aging concerns.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggdXUFd4O9B_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggdXUFd4O9B_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s5img.png"},{"type":"html","id":"gg0TMPe4VmS_text","label":"gg0TMPe4VmS_text","default":"<p>What they don't want you to know is that they aren't in control of your aging...YOU are.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggZthUHEInP_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggZthUHEInP_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s5img.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggKIkER_mKL_text","label":"ggKIkER_mKL_text","default":"<p>And that the key to youthful, firm skin is actually SIMPLE... and something EVERYONE has access to.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggB9YXtmlq3_text","label":"ggB9YXtmlq3_text","default":"<p><strong>And it all starts with Progerin control.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gghU0ILXFYa_text","label":"gghU0ILXFYa_text","default":"<p>Okay, on to the good news.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggmLZwzA-P1_text","label":"ggmLZwzA-P1_text","default":"<p>Once I realized the importance of controlling this aging protein, I began to look at skin aging in a completely different way.</p>"}],
